OL,4,BChristophe Berra: Captain 'hurt and
OL,5,Bangry' at having no future at Hearts
OL,6, Captain Christophe Berra says he is
OL,7, "hurt and angry" after being told he
OL,8, can leave Hearts and instructed to
OL,9, train with the reserves.
OL,11,FThe 34-year-old centre-back had been a
OL,12,Fregular this season until being dropped
OL,13,Fby new manager Daniel Stendel for the
OL,14,Fdraw with Aberdeen on 29 December.
OL,16,FBerra still has 18 months left on the
OL,17,Fcontract he signed under Craig Levein
OL,18,Fin summer 2018 but will be allowed to
OL,19,Fdepart either on loan or permanently.
OL,21,F"It came out the blue," Berra said.
